rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0001
rows.name:
You made me wait quite
a while, rookies.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0002
rows.name: Sorry for this!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0003
rows.name:
It's Vandham's fault for
rushing off without us.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0004
rows.name: Ha ha ha! Sorry about that.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0005
rows.name:
You probably met him during our
fight earlier, but let me give
him a proper introduction.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0006
rows.name: My name is Suzaku! I'm Vandham's Blade.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0007
rows.name:
Looking forward to
working with you all.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0008
rows.name: Likewise!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0009
rows.name:
That weapon you use is
quite unique, isn't it?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0010
rows.name:
They're called Dual Scythes.
Vandham's pretty much the only one
around here who can handle them.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0011
rows.name: Wow, you're really something, mister...

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0012
rows.name: Hahahah!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0013
rows.name:
Don't praise him too much.
He'll get carried away.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0014
rows.name:
So Vandham-san, you only
have the one Blade?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0015
rows.name: Yeah, pretty much.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0016
rows.name:
Most people have two or three for
tactical flexibility, but I'm
strong enough with just Suzaku!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0017
rows.name: You're even more impressive now...

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0018
rows.name: Hahahah!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0019
rows.name:
Sounds to me like you just can't
be bothered to think up more than
one strategy, eh, old man?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0020
rows.name: Gahahah!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0021
rows.name:
Well, now that Suzaku's
introduction is done, let's
get to the main topic.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0022
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] He's changing the subject...

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0023
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] He's steering the
conversation elsewhere.
